Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.00,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.42,0:00:07.32,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是上回故事的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:10.34,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士在和貓先生一起修行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著上啊亮士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.09,0:00:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 涼子她?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:27.15,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 我們繼續講述御伽銀行最大的危機
